    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_jm.00094.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>  
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden<ptr target="loc.08016_n1"/></name>
                    <date when="1891-03-22">P M March 22 '91</date>
                </dateline> 
            </opener>
            <p>No worse&#8212;just taken a small cup of cocoa&#8212;sent off MS of "old actors in N Y"<ptr target="loc.07640_n6"/> 
                to Truth weekly,<ptr target="loc.08016_n5"/> &#36;16<ptr target="loc.08016_n2"/>&#8212;the 
                Doctor<ptr target="loc.08039_n2"/> has just been&#8212;upon the whole he thinks 
                things satisfactory&#8212;I am whacking away valiantly (I suppose) with pen 
                &#38; ink&#8212;weather dark &#38; sullen&#8212;death all around us<ptr target="loc.08016_n6"/>&#8212;
            </p> 
            <closer> 
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc_jm.00095.jpg" type="verso"/>
        </body>
